    description: "A cooking recipe with ingredients and steps."
    shapeIndex: 3
    mamlText: "{\n  title: \"Verona's Special Goat Milk\"\n  servings: 6\n  prep_time: \"59 minutes\"\n  cook_time: \"71 minutes\"\n\n  # Ingredients\n  ingredients: [\n    \"2 cups passionfruit\"\n    \"2 cups rosemary\"\n    \"1 tsp quinoa\"\n    \"3 pieces mozzarella\"\n    \"1 cups kohlrabi\"\n  ]\n\n  # Instructions\n  steps: [\n    \"A delightful tart combining tender endive and sweet juniper berry, set in a buttery pastry shell and finished with a hint of five spice.\"\n    \"Hearty white wine and pigeon stew, slow-cooked with annatto seed and spinach for a comforting, flavorful meal.\"\n    \"A delightful tart combining creamy kale and sweet cherry, set in a buttery pastry shell and finished with a hint of tarragon.\"\n    \"A classic pie filled with delicious crocodile and smoky mustard, baked in a tender pastry crust and topped with a golden-brown lattice.\"\n    \"Fresh mixed greens tossed with dhansak-rubbed salmon, garlic, and a light dressing.\"\n    \"Hearty peaches and beef stew, slow-cooked with saffron and brussels sprouts for a comforting, flavorful meal.\"\n    \"Hearty spelt bread and chicken stew, slow-cooked with kaffir leaves and beetroot for a comforting, flavorful meal.\"\n  ]\n\n  nutrition: {\n    calories: 544\n    protein: \"48g\"\n    carbs: \"90g\"\n    fat: \"27g\"\n  }\n}"
  }
